settings.html:
<style>

html,body{
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

/**Manu Section **/

.menu-list .elementor-icon-list-icon{
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    line-height: 25px;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 0px;
    background: #222831;
    margin-right: 15px
    }
  
.menu-list .elementor-icon-list-item:hover .elementor-icon-list-icon{
    background: #AD2121;
    
}   
    
.menu-list .elementor-icon-list-icon svg{
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    
    }
    
    
.menu-list .elementor-icon-list-item{
    border-radius: 0px !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
   margin-bottom: 30px !important;
}  


/**Hero Section**/

@media only screen and (max-width: 1024px){

.fancy-text .premium-fancy-text{
    font-size: 48px !important;
    line-height: 58px !important;
}

}


/**ABout Section **/

.shapes-about{
    
    animation: aboutAmini linear 2s infinite alternate;
    -webkit-animation: aboutAmini linear 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes aboutAmini {
  from {
    transform: scale(1);
    -webkit-transform: scale(1);
    -moz-transform: scale(1);
    -ms-transform: scale(1);
    -o-transform: scale(1);
  }

  to {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    -webkit-transform: scale(1.1);
    -moz-transform: scale(1.1);
    -ms-transform: scale(1.1);
    -o-transform: scale(1.1);
  }
}

/**Portfolio **/

.portfolio-text{
    background: linear-gradient( 0deg, rgba(2, 5, 10, 1) 0%, rgba(2, 5, 10, 0.5802696078431373) 61%, rgba(2, 5, 10, 0) 100% );
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: bottom;
    transition: all linear 0.3s;
    -webkit-transition: all linear 0.3s;
} 

.portfolio-box:hover .portfolio-text{
    transform: scaleY(1);
}



/** Maruee Section **/

.marquee-content {
    white-space: nowrap;
    display: flex;
    width: 100000px;
    transform: translateX(0px);
    animation: marquee 22s linear infinite;
    
}

@keyframes marquee {
    
    100%  {transform:translateX(-2799.31px)
   }
   
}


/** Menu Active**/



.menu-highlight .active a .elementor-icon-list-text{
   color: #AD2121!important;
}

.menu-highlight .active .elementor-icon-list-icon{
    background-color: #AD2121;
}


</style>


<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script>
var className = 'menu-highlight',
    $ =jQuery,
    clickLock = false
$(document).ready(function(){
$('.' + className + ' .elementor-icon-list-item').on('click', function(){
    $('.' + className + ' .elementor-icon-list-item').removeClass('active')
    $(this).addClass('active')
    clickLock = true
    setTimeout(function(){
        clickLock = false
    },500)
})
})
$(window).on('load scroll', function(){
    
    if( clickLock ) return
    
    var ids = [],
        id
    
    $('.elementor-top-section, [data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .e-con, [data-elementor-type="wp-page"] > .e-container').each(function(){
        if($(window).scrollTop() + $(window).height() - 350 > $(this).offset().top){
            ids.push($(this).attr('id'))
        }
    })
    
    ids = ids.filter(element => {
      return element !== undefined
    })
    
    id = ids[ids.length - 1]
    
    $('.elementor-icon-list-item').removeClass('active')
    $('[href="#'+id+'"]').parent().addClass('active')
})
</script>
